{"tid":1094291,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"點同00後表弟講Apink當年有幾勁？","createTime":"2019-04-06T07:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T18:37:57.000Z","uid":1369,"like":27,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"55cdd257feb206cc012f07b4bc4f19d08f410d8a","tid":1094291,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:50:19.000Z","msg":"今日同親戚拜山，同枱嘅表弟今年係咁講izone 有幾勁，幾靚，牙權有幾大波。我心諗apink真係勁過多多聲。當年佢無論牙瓏、恩地、娜恩等等都一流；10年前首mr chu nonono 真係聽到我哇哇聲<br />\n<br />\n上節目打歌個人同團隊榮譽都攞哂，最緊要係a pink  真正比我知道乜係「kpop」，一班panda一齊相約去睇show，一齊學應援，一齊整deepfake，係真正享受追星嘅趣味。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，以izone既人氣黎講，佢真係超班；但經歷過a pink 年代的我絕對唔會覺得izone已經上左神枱。"},{"pid":"a0ccfc7d844ff2dd3ea64675f1fdd506fb710619","tid":1094291,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:54:11.000Z","msg":"deepfake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d927c32cbb40e1078ba2964916f9c52d6c38ece9","tid":1094291,"uid":29660,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:57:44.000Z","msg":"有冇同表弟講你喺連登娛樂台係過街老鼠<br />\n同佢講下你有幾勁仲好啦"},{"pid":"e030a2bd212fae6b749160c8b3fd1c45ff0d7568","tid":1094291,"uid":245910,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:59:12.000Z","msg":"牙你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5b848559080cb9b36b2b9c254cd846dac0c028","tid":1094291,"uid":65429,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:30:28.000Z","msg":"點同90後表弟講少女時代當年有幾勁？"},{"pid":"cd27d54fa1f0953e74bbf844839d374530da0836","tid":1094291,"uid":152432,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:54:13.000Z","msg":"咁都係得兩首歌姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，雖然當時真係紅到可以同少時打"},{"pid":"cd416c964bd7964c5ea48bebd030fa40577522f8","tid":1094291,"uid":58335,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:58:58